:Multiplier
1, Price Multiplier: %Base% |STVR=%Base%||Base=0|<br><br> {Loop~%Rolls%,{If~{And~{Dice~1d20} = 1,%MagicItems%!=2} ? [SpecificWeapons] / {If~%OnlyRanged%=1 ? [Weapons=90] / [Weapons]}}}

:MyItemPrice
1,{Round~2,{Calc~(%STVR%+%Base%)*%ItemMultiplier%}} gp
