5,It has a piercing end [WoW Materials.WeaponMetals], a haft [WoodOrSteel] and a handle wrapped with [WoW Materials.HiltMaterial].
6,It has a haft made of [WoW Materials.Woods] and a blade made of [WoW Materials.WeaponMetals]
7,It is [WoW Materials.WeaponMetals]
8,It has a haft [WoodOrSteel] and a slashing end [WoW Materials.WeaponMetals]
9,From the horizontal hilt wrapped in [WoW Materials.HiltMaterial] extend 5 claws [WoW Materials.WeaponMetals]
10,It is made of [WoW Materials.Woods] with a pocket made of [WoW Materials.HiltMaterial]
11,Protruding from a center made of [WoW Materials.Woods] are 3 curved blades [WoW Materials.WeaponMetals]
12,It is made from braided [WoW Materials.HiltMaterial].

